locations.title: Clothes Helping Kids - Albuquerque
locations.description:
Clothes Helping Kids has been providing financial assistance to disadvantaged children in central and northern New Mexico since 2000. The organization schedules daily pickups of donated items in certain New Mexico communities and distributes them.

Clothes Helping Kids accepts clothes, homewares, and other misc items. If you're not sure whether they'll accept your donation, please give them a call beforehand.
